                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The nosferatu can cast <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Dominate]{Dominate}</em> at will as a divine innate spell. Casting it requires staring into the target's eyes, giving the spell the visual trait. The save DC is 29, and a creature that succeeds is temporarily immune to that nosferatu's Dominate for 24 hours.</p>\n<p>Fully destroying the nosferatu ends the domination, but merely reducing the nosferatu to 0 HP is insufficient to break the spell.</p>"
