                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:29]</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 day</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 2} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Doomed]{Doomed 1}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 3}, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 3} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Doomed]{Doomed 2}, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained 3}, and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 3} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> unconscious (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 6</strong> death</p>"
